{"tid":2364290,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"【動森SCP】SCP 426 我是一個烤麵包機 I am a Toaster","createTime":"2021-01-13T01:10:55.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-13T01:10:55.000Z","uid":129010,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"b09d98000437f17a3860d21a25852800e7df554c","tid":2364290,"uid":129010,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-13T01:10:55.000Z","msg":"有無人知SCP基金會？今次試下用動森整SCP的收容物同故事<br />\n<br />\n【動森SCP】SCP 426 我是一個烤麵包機 I am a Toaster<br />\n描述：你好，我是SCP-426。我必須藉由這樣的描述方式避免歧異。我跟普通的烤吐司機功能一樣，通電後就能拿來烤吐司。但任何人在提及我時，都會下意識地用第一人稱稱呼我。儘管已經有了多次的嘗試，目前仍未找到規避此異常效應的書寫或口述方法。在我周遭超過兩個月後，個體會開始認為自己也是烤吐司機。除非被他人阻止，否則受影響者將會因為模仿我的標準功能而受到嚴重傷害。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/yZEdIQMjsAQ\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FyZEdIQMjsAQ&d=Eu1QSTPz0OFPBNy7%2BevvEX4WTS3z8ocQ7DCXl2btf88%3D&h=00397d17\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/yZEdIQMjsAQ</a><br />\n<br />\n影片截圖<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/esRyTjJ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FesRyTjJ.png&h=b3a31600&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/0phm2c4.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F0phm2c4.png&h=8470f7dc&s={SIZE}\" />"}]}